{"tid":597251,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"女友一句 全車靜哂","createTime":"2018-03-18T12:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T13:47:27.000Z","uid":89134,"like":3,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8661d2692a7d11c657df8b5b29140578fd33feaf","tid":597251,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:36:04.000Z","msg":"小弟有一day由旺角返屋企，由於太夜，因此要搭亡命小巴<br />\n在小巴上坐在司機後的一對情侶，在上車後不斷鬧交。<br />\n女的不斷鬧男是仆x，而男則鬧女的是死八婆。<br />\n經過15分鐘的「口部對戰」，男的終於忍不到，講了一句粗口。<br />\n<br />\n男︰「正臭x，講極都唔明，正臭x（x為粗口也）」<br />\n女︰「如果真系臭，咁你又『奶』」<br />\n<br />\n突然全車靜晒，司機減速駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n各位男士要講粗口鬧人要三思<br />\n免得把生活公諸於世。"},{"pid":"841993432895f95e0c2726214794abb3f508296a","tid":597251,"uid":149792,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:37:07.000Z","msg":"樓豬啱啱出泥？"},{"pid":"9b003856691db8f2561291d5bc2f359c9e5ab521","tid":597251,"uid":89134,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"841993432895f95e0c2726214794abb3f508296a","tid":597251,"uid":149792,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:37:07.000Z","msg":"樓豬啱啱出泥？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:38:13.000Z","msg":"啱啱學行"},{"pid":"403d7ae36f0dc4f41ac391794c7a3ec1affd5b6d","tid":597251,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9b003856691db8f2561291d5bc2f359c9e5ab521","tid":597251,"uid":89134,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"841993432895f95e0c2726214794abb3f508296a","tid":597251,"uid":149792,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:37:07.000Z","msg":"樓豬啱啱出泥？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:38:13.000Z","msg":"啱啱學行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b870a13e38106c605ba4aae337864b841c351d1","tid":597251,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"403d7ae36f0dc4f41ac391794c7a3ec1affd5b6d","tid":597251,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid"